snippet.title: Sunday chat ,the bies lies on Manson and Johnny's case. Victim mentality and corrupt system .
snippet.description: Why Ambers friends were texting pictures of knives to her? why would you do that before meeting your husband for dinner . Why they said " you dont have to use it ,just show it to him " ? Plus remember the time when Ambere recorder him trying to cut himself and she used this in court to make him look crazy and dangerous . Why nobody in the UK looked into this. I am not playing the audio of Johnny trying to self harm because I dont think is right and is heart breaking but we can still chat about it . Sorry it took 2 plus hours . The next thing is the false allegations of Ashley Morgan against Manson and how this makes zero sense,their stories changed all the time and shame on People's magazine for giving her a cover !,she produced fake pictures and talks about things that CANNOT be proven . These two cases are related ,if you dont think so then you are not paying attention .  #johnnydeppisinnocent #mansonisinnocent #justiceforjohnny #evanrachelwood #amberheard #marilynmansoncase #ashleymorganlies #metoo #domesticviolencelies
